column2: SELECT count(*) FROM GalSpecLine AS g  JOIN SpecPhoto AS sp ON sp.specobjid = g.specobjid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq(#,#,#) AS GN  ON GN.specobjID = g.specobjid JOIN Galaxy as gal ON gal.specobjId = g.specobjid WHERE  h_alpha_eqw between # and # and oii_#_eqw between # and # and sp.modelMag_g-sp.modelMag_i > # and sp.z between # and # and sp.modelMag_i-#*log1#(#E+#*sp.z) < # and gal.petroR9#_i/g.petroR5#_i > #
